Description: Albuminoidal substances; modified starches; glues; enzymes

Subentries.Description: Prepared glues and other prepared adhesives, not elsewhere specified or included; products suitable for use as glues or adhesives, put up for retail sale as glues or adhesives, not exceeding a net weight of 1 kg:
Products suitable for use as glues or adhesives, put up for retail sale as glues or adhesives, not exceeding a net weight of 1 kg:
Animal glue, including casein glue, but not including fish glue
Adhesives based on polymers of headings 3901 to 3913 or on rubber:
Optically clear free-film adhesives and optically clear curable liquid adhesives of a kind used solely or principally for the manufacture of flat panel displays or touch-sensitive screen panels
